r-season-with-split-squad-weekend</guid><category>Track &amp; Field</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Audrey Thomas" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/3/19/JLS_5638.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The West Virginia University track and field team opens the outdoor season with a split-squad weekend on March 20-21. The Mountaineers will host the Marty Pushkin Invitational in Morgantown while another group travels to Tampa, Fla., to compete in the USF Alumni Invitational.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/19/JLS_5638.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/19/JLS_5638.jpg"><media:title>Audrey Thomas</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/19/JLS_5638.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 12:35:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>16</s:sport_id><s:story_id>58892</s:story_id></item><item><title>Six Mountaineers Set to Compete at 2026 NCAA Wrestling Championships</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/18/six-mountaineers-set-to-compete-at-2026-ncaa-wrestling-championships</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/18/six-mountaineers-set-to-compete-at-2026-ncaa-wrestling-championships</guid><category>Wrestling</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Rocket Arena (2026 NCAA Wrestling Championships)" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/3/18/_YNX8064.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – Six Mountaineers from the West Virginia University wrestling team are set to compete in the 2026 NCAA Wrestling Championships on March 19-21, at Rocket Arena in Cleveland.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/18/_YNX8064.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/18/_YNX8064.jpg"><media:title>Rocket Arena (2026 NCAA Wrestling Championships)</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/18/_YNX8064.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 16:46:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>18</s:sport_id><s:story_id>58891</s:story_id></item><item><title>West Virginia Set to Host BYU</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/18/baseball-west-virginia-set-to-host-byu</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/18/baseball-west-virginia-set-to-host-byu</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Matchup vs. BYU 2026" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/3/18/BB26_Matchup_1920x1080_BYU.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The No. 20 West Virginia University baseball team is back at home for a three-game series against Big 12 foe BYU, March 19-21. First pitch on Thursday is set for 4:30 p.m., Friday for 2 p.m., and Saturday for 12:30 p.m.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/18/BB26_Matchup_1920x1080_BYU.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/18/BB26_Matchup_1920x1080_BYU.jpg"><media:title>Matchup vs. BYU 2026</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/image